acm.graphics

Class GRectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • acm.graphics.GRectangle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class GRectangle
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class is a double-precision version of the Rectangle class in java.awt.
    See Also:
